<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>ZPanel: Confirm Email Update</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}!</h1>
    <p>We received a request to update your email address on the ZPanel platform.</p>
    <p>If you made this request, please confirm by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{url}}">Confirm Email Update</a></p>
    <p>If you did not request this change, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
    <p>Thank you for using ZPanel!</p>
</body>
</html>